CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper February 8, 1947, pg. 17, reads: "Sisters Get Honors - A double birthday party was given last week by Mr. and Mrs. Walter Jackson of 20-B Hawkins Valley, Rankin, for their daughters, Elsa and Jacqueline. Movies and games entertained the guests. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Children wearing party hats gathered around sisters Elsa Jackson and Jacqueline Jackson seated behind tiered cake for joint birthday party in home of Walter Jackson, Rankin
